00:15:06,022 --> 00:15:07,489
So, I thought maybe...

267
00:15:07,657 --> 00:15:09,491
Similar...
Bennett, the real Bennett...

268
00:15:09,798 --> 00:15:11,785
would use an Active to...

269
00:15:11,953 --> 00:15:13,153
You thought...

270
00:15:15,577 --> 00:15:17,212
That's idiotic.

271
00:15:18,219 --> 00:15:19,751
Actives are beautiful.

272
00:15:21,029 --> 00:15:21,920
Yeah.

273
00:15:28,162 --> 00:15:29,469
And it's not my evil plan.

274
00:15:29,637 --> 00:15:31,007
It's-It's not evil.

275
00:15:31,132 --> 00:15:32,297
Wait. Hey!

276
00:15:32,651 --> 00:15:33,932
I'm just here for Echo.

277
00:15:34,736 --> 00:15:37,468
My last ethical quandary was...

278
00:15:38,536 --> 00:15:39,578
unhelpful.

279
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:41,690
Let mommy and daddy
do the squabbling.

280
00:15:46,612 --> 00:15:47,529
Yes, sir.

281
00:15:47,697 --> 00:15:48,747
Right away.

282
00:15:51,017 --> 00:15:52,367
Looks like you got the girl.

283
00:15:53,366 --> 00:15:55,677
Let me go check on...
is it "Echo"?...

284
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,372
and get everything signed.

285
00:15:57,696 --> 00:16:00,709
Can I use your phone?
Just wanna check in with my House.

286
00:16:01,108 --> 00:16:02,542
Yes, of course.

287
00:16:14,145 --> 00:16:15,245
Wasabi peas.

288
00:16:16,595 --> 00:16:18,327
I'm excited and scared.

289
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,440
Finally!

290
00:16:26,565 --> 00:16:28,038
<i>Everything good there?</i>

291
00:16:28,499 --> 00:16:30,556
Everything's great, me-man,

292
00:16:30,681 --> 00:16:33,631
except I've got
a long white beard from waiting.

293
00:16:34,327 --> 00:16:35,762
Put the signal through.

294
00:16:42,525 --> 00:16:43,599
Solid.

295
00:16:44,295 --> 00:16:45,671
I see what you see.

296
00:16:47,154 --> 00:16:49,901
I still don't know how I'm gonna get
Perrin's brain map running,

297
